{"type":"article_comment","id":124746,"parentType":"article","parentId":9050,"uid":14934,"contents":"我也来献丑写个：<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nDear (学生会名字)<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nAs you may know, recently the police broke into the campus of Hong Kong Polytechnic University and arrested many students. Dozens of students were injured. Doctors and first-aiders were not allowed to help the injured students and even got arrested (<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9qb3NodWF3b25nY2Yvc3RhdHVzLzExOTYzOTY4MTU3MjcyODQyMjQ\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1196396815727284224</a>). Until now, more than 100 students are still being trapped in the campus without food and water.<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nBeing shocked by the violence in the campus, AStA TU Berlin has sent an letter to all TU Berlin students and call for solidarity( <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/astatuberlin/posts/untrusted fake 2049bbsrlin/posts/2930301143670191</a>) with Hong Kong students. The university should be a place for studying and keeping the students safe. I hope you could stand with Hong Kong students as well.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPLEASE STAND WITH HONG KONG STUDENTS. PLEASE SHOW SOLIDARITY WITH HONG KONG STUDENTS.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSomeone who cares about Hong Kong students and human Rights.\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n</a><div class=\"meta\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/astatuberlin/posts/untrusted fake 2049bbsrlin/posts/2930301143670191</a>) with Hong Kong students. The university should be a place for studying and keeping the students safe. I hope you could stand with Hong Kong students as well.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPLEASE STAND WITH HONG KONG STUDENTS. PLEASE SHOW SOLIDARITY WITH HONG KONG STUDENTS.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSomeone who cares about Hong Kong students and human Rights.\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n<span class=\"pull-right aw-sma